title: Black Nike Air Force
description:
WMNS Air Max 90 “Rose Pink” is another colorway of the iconic runner, released to celebrate its 30th anniversary.
Using the same OG color blocking as the “Infrared” model, the pair combines white and particle grey on a mesh and leather upper.
Bright pink accents are applied throughout, while a white midsole and a black-and-pink rubber outsole complete the design.
